446
00:34:51,090 --> 00:34:54,120
- Why did you come to this back street shop?
- What?

447
00:34:54,120 --> 00:34:56,920
You and I both have to do this without getting caught.

448
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:59,020
We should do a safe transaction.

449
00:34:59,020 --> 00:35:01,130
That being the case,

450
00:35:01,130 --> 00:35:03,110
we have to spend a lot of expenses.

451
00:35:03,110 --> 00:35:06,770
It's the cost for the safe transaction.

452
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:12,350
Then, why don't we meet in the middle?

453
00:35:12,350 --> 00:35:16,640
Pay me 47.5 million won per kilogram.

454
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:21,980
Sure, let's do that. 47.5 million won.

455
00:35:21,990 --> 00:35:25,900
By the way,

456
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:31,470
how much would you give me for this?

457
00:35:41,610 --> 00:35:46,470
For this, I'll think good for you,

458
00:35:46,470 --> 00:35:50,860
and give you 300 million won.

459
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:58,570
300 million won?

460
00:35:58,590 --> 00:36:00,580
Then, I'll sell this one too.

461
00:36:00,580 --> 00:36:03,750
Please do the safe transaction.

462
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:16,780
Since this was my old man's safe,

463
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:19,410
I bet the secret code was passed down from him too.

464
00:36:19,410 --> 00:36:23,460
Then would it be the old man's birthday?

465
00:36:27,950 --> 00:36:30,480
It isn't the one.

466
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:33,810
What about Young Gook's birthday?

467
00:36:33,810 --> 00:36:35,610
Are you home, Chairman?

468
00:36:35,610 --> 00:36:37,710
Please give them to me.

469
00:36:37,710 --> 00:36:41,680
- What did you buy so much?
- These are clothes and shoes for the kids.

470
00:36:48,970 --> 00:36:51,510
What are you doing, Ajumma?

471
00:36:51,540 --> 00:36:54,350
Why are you here, Ajumma!

472
00:36:54,350 --> 00:36:58,060
That is... I was cleaning!

473
00:36:58,060 --> 00:37:00,580
I was so thankful that you let me live here,

474
00:37:00,580 --> 00:37:03,980
so I tried to clean your study at least.

475
00:37:03,980 --> 00:37:05,670
Cleaning?

476
00:37:05,670 --> 00:37:07,700
You are doing that?

477
00:37:07,700 --> 00:37:10,320
Do you expect me to believe that?

478
00:37:10,320 --> 00:37:12,730
What's the reason for you coming into this room?

479
00:37:12,730 --> 00:37:14,880
I said, cleaning!

480
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:18,340
I'm really here to clean!

481
00:37:18,340 --> 00:37:21,600
Madam!

482
00:37:21,600 --> 00:37:25,340
You promised not to be seen by the Chairman.

483
00:37:25,340 --> 00:37:27,640
Ah, really.

484
00:37:33,660 --> 00:37:38,070
Why was I living with that enemy Ajumma?

485
00:37:38,070 --> 00:37:42,520
Why can't I remember it? Why!

486
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:47,210
My goodness! Seriously!

487
00:37:47,210 --> 00:37:51,260
Madam, how can you go into Chairman's study?

488
00:37:51,260 --> 00:37:54,690
What if Chairman says you should get out of the house again?

489
00:37:54,690 --> 00:37:56,140
Chief Jo!

490
00:37:56,140 --> 00:37:59,590
Find out the passcode for the safe in the study!

491
00:37:59,590 --> 00:38:02,820
But Madam! It's not the right time to do that.

492
00:38:02,820 --> 00:38:05,280
Also, It's not like they are going anywhere!

493
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:11,410
Besides, if you get kicked out figuring that out, what good would that do?

494
00:38:11,410 --> 00:38:13,580
Seriously!

495
00:38:14,820 --> 00:38:19,550
Did she take it out on me just now?

496
00:38:19,550 --> 00:38:22,010
Okay, fine.

497
00:38:22,010 --> 00:38:25,380
It's not like they'd go anywhere other than the safe in the study.

498
00:38:25,380 --> 00:38:28,000
Of course.

499
00:39:17,990 --> 00:39:20,540
Mi Rim.

500
00:39:24,470 --> 00:39:28,180
