502
00:39:31,450 --> 00:39:33,290
I'm not a pervert.

503
00:39:33,290 --> 00:39:36,360
Please believe me, Mi Rim.

504
00:39:37,590 --> 00:39:42,250
I know that you are not a pervert.

505
00:39:42,250 --> 00:39:47,000
And I think you are pretty cool.

506
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:50,040
